    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for, so it's totally ready for its next adventure! It runs super smooth and looks great inside and out. If you're looking for a reliable, comfy car that\u2019s ready to go today, you've found it! Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
