      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offered here is a stunning example of a well-cared-for vehicle that strikes the ideal balance between everyday utility and refined performance. The exterior paint presents beautifully with a high-gloss finish, showing only the expected, minor signs of light use consistent with careful driving. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the seats are firm and supportive, the dashboard is free of cracks or fading, and every switchgear provides that satisfying, tactile click. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs whisper-quiet at idle, providing robust acceleration when called upon. We have recently completed a comprehensive multi-point inspection, including a fluid flush and brake pad replacement, ensuring this car is turn-key ready for its next owner. With a full service history included, you can purchase with confidence knowing this car has been treated with the respect it deserves.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
